title: Remodeled Stevens Sq Studio MCAD
posting_body: ['Stevens Sq Remodeled Studio Apt; MCAD, walk to downtown, MCTC, UMN', 'Property Address', '1905 Stevens Ave. SO.', '|  203 | Minneapolis, MN 55403', 'Available: 08/01/2022 & 09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Gardner Investments, Inc. |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'This unit is around 366 square feet and comes with a newly remodeled kitchen with a breakfast bar, bathroom, and walk in closet.', 'We allow one person occupancy.', 'We allow cats and dogs  for additional  rent and a one time $200.00 non refundable pet deposit.', 'Off-street parking may be available for an additional charge.', 'This is a smoke free property.', 'We require a $45.00 application fee per adult when applying.', 'Income must be 2.0 x the rent.', 'No Evictions or UD’s in the last 5 years.', 'No major credit accounts written off, delinquent, or in collections in last 5 years.', 'No felony convictions in the last five years or Misdemeanors in the last year.', 'Those with felonies for murder, rape, arson, or assault will be denied.', 'No major lease violations from previous Landlord references.', 'We accept first time renters and co-signers.', 'Go to <URL> to set up a viewing or to apply on line.', ' You will also find our other fine offerings there.', 'Units vary', 'Amenities', 'Remodeled kitchen', 'Renovated units', 'hardwood floors', 'natural woodwork', 'breakfast bar', 'on-line rent payment', 'On site Laundry Facility', 'On direct bus line to West Bank', 'secured entry', 'on site management', '24 hour emergency service', 'surveillance camera', '5 minute walk to downtown', 'located a block from Eat Street', '2 blocks from MCAD', 'off-street parking', 'MCTC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 366', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent starts at $775.00', 'Available:  9/1/22', 'Application Fee: $45.00', 'Security Deposit: $775.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
